node.text: I’m obsessed with this new Blueberry Protein Waffles recipe I just whipped up with @dishitgirldina and our littles love them too! Want to know the secret? @hphood Cottage Cheese with Blueberry, which gives them that perfect blueberry flavor and tons of protein. This year, @hphood is taking cottage cheese recipes head to head through The Cottage Cheese Delicious Duels. Reminder to cast your vote for your favorite recipe in the bracket at deliciousduels.hood.com. For each vote, @hphood will donate one 16 oz. tub of cottage cheese (up to 5,000 tubs) to @foodbankofcny (Food Bank of Central NY) and @gr8bosfoodbank (The Greater Boston Food Bank). Go vote!! #deliciousduels #hoodcottagecheese #ad
